o y eficaz,con Andrea,Marta y Irene siempre me resuelven todas las dudas y me ayudan en lo que necesite,encantado,un placer como siempre","time":1685617233,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Isabel Millán","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115313310199538956844/reviews","language":"es","original_language":"es","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/AAcHTtdUMfaP--JCYfNjveo8XEXJCRU2plVMC_gWxi6WBGZF=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"Hace 1 mes","text":"Nos ha gustado mucho el trato recibido. Hemos sido atendidos muy amablemente por Marta. Si algún otro día necesito este servicio, seguro que volveré.","time":1683381456,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Berta Lemus","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103028366522214955197/reviews","language":"es","original_language":"es","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/AAcHTteWXLwM28DCjt07kw-BHOt7Fny2er0vvRNy4W1qfarJ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"Hace una semana","text":"He sido atendida por Andrea y su trato ha sido genial. Realiza su trabajo de manera excelente.","time":1687545171,"translated":false}],"types":["jewelry_store","finance","store","point_of_interest","establishment"],"url":"https://maps.google.com/?cid=13882353097699614927","user_ratings_total":458,"utc_offset":120,"vicinity":"Avenida de Andalucía, 18, Sevilla","website":"https://quickgold.es/tiendas/compro-oro-sevilla/avenida-de-andalucia-18/?utm_source=gmb&utm_medium=boton&utm_content&utm_campaign=sitio-web-gmb","wheelchair_accessible_entrance":true},"status":"OK"},"tienda2Google":{"html_attributions":[],"result":{"address_components":[{"long_name":"43","short_name":"43","types":["street_number"]},{"long_name":"Calle San Eloy","short_name":"C. San Eloy","types":["route"]},{"long_name":"Sevilla","short_name":"Sevilla","types":["locality","political"]},{"long_name":"Sevilla","short_name":"SE","types":["administrative_area_level_